{"tid":1425151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] [未fact check]大陸仲派緊人落嚟打鳩香港人","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:08:53.000Z","uid":88084,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81f81ccea56df2f1353bd4036a24a08db8046ed6","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"事源：今晚同朋友雙排打pubg，同兩個大陸佬組隊玩。<br />\n<br />\n一開始大陸佬狂聊我同朋友講嘢，問我哋香港邊度人，仲話「兄弟，我尖沙咀的。（普通話）」<br />\n<br />\n我同朋友仲以為佢哋係假膠，傾傾吓發現好似堅料黎：<br />\n1. 佢地話自己喺福建落嚟，係北角青年會嘅人。<br />\n2. 佢地話覺得香港好亂，部分人無收錢落嚟「幫香港手」，叫我同朋友無事就唔好出街。<br />\n3. 佢地話仲有兄弟搭船落緊嚟，暫時未知有咩行動，等緊消息。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\nps 我同朋友都add咗嗰兩個大陸人做friend，聽晚睇吓可唔可以再chok多啲料"},{"pid":"bfb3160ee74036320a750a6c883c6742b02dacfe","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e2f760e00857536d1c5cee1c2f07f909e7ac8aa7","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1ac72ae6f01a8ec3eb405dd7333a308a3b249463","tid":1425151,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d04e935af4a1ec5f16f11228bef8a7b0ea9c58e3","tid":1425151,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"隻狗一日係個籠到一日都聲大大"},{"pid":"9f9f0bb1ade37ce46b077f9040bf60eeb789fcd7","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"估唔到打鋪機都同到大陸佬攞料，有打機嘅巴絲呢排識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ba5ceb88dd39de1c93d4561ad7cba2eac9be3e","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點：仲有福建佬坐船落緊嚟</span></strong>"},{"pid":"faed8bb2c023e62722deab72a7f57465ed36a687","tid":1425151,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor